{"tid":1425741,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"情緒困擾 終於鼓起勇氣準備去睇醫生 啱啱send咗信畀公司求體諒","createTime":"2019-08-06T20:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T12:27:13.000Z","uid":152123,"like":78,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"23a6f8643af157a69e12b004867f516de3423c8e","tid":1425741,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:12:05.000Z","msg":"呢幾個月嚟 食唔安 瞓唔落<br />\n其實以前本身都有啲抑鬱症狀 但唔嚴重影響生活就一直由得佢<br />\n<br />\n但呢排真係完全無法專注工作<br />\n特別係香港發生咁多事 我相信香港人發夢定係睇直播都寢食難安<br />\n提唔起勁去做嘢 真係只要一諗到個deadline就痛苦到唔想做<br />\n今晚又睇怕眼光光望天光<br />\n<br />\n龜縮多年 終於鼓起勇氣準備去睇醫生<br />\n同埋話畀公司知件事 睇下會唔會有咩安排可以幫到手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點都好 我曾經係連登應承過大家唔會自殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1282732\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1282732</a><br />\n我希望有情緒困擾嘅你睇到呢度 都會同我一齊鼓起勇氣去面對<br />\n人總需要勇敢生存啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dedeff5f42258067d2b7dc23fbcdb84dec702a81","tid":1425741,"uid":55759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:13:00.000Z","msg":"Add oil"},{"pid":"f364a02268068cfc8f52aadcad67e6d6fd4de3d1","tid":1425741,"uid":28921,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:13:37.000Z","msg":"加油啊，我要每年都同你互相講新年快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e8e802391a566aea85a207d8802aac05b3774e6","tid":1425741,"uid":210995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:13:58.000Z","msg":"我會係你樹窿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c519e5adcea733c5593f97566e125411b3f150e","tid":1425741,"uid":152123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:14:56.000Z","msg":"明天的我一定會比今天更強大"},{"pid":"05fb5879c3f83712a8f8a39f52a1c29fbfa43a82","tid":1425741,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:26:55.000Z","msg":"渣渣揮"},{"pid":"0d204590216ded32e24a5d3ee69b826435900eac","tid":1425741,"uid":120412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:39:03.000Z","msg":"開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nlink:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/OY6xwlZRBnmlPaCATObKog\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOY6xwlZRBnmlPaCATObKog&d=%2FAyHQi%2FQiMXiPJLA4RPCZlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=2439a22a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/OY6xwlZRBnmlPaCATObKog</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比個template 大家<br />\n如果想朋友來取暖，請send 比佢地睇下<br />\n記得講  發夢想發未發 唔講<br />\n只發洩不指責不論陣型"},{"pid":"4efdd4d03975632d5f2abc8dbfdb6ace5c923fd8","tid":1425741,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:09:13.000Z","msg":"有冇平醫生推薦 睇唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e51a235a4fb114d99926e3e6dd0e0d1528014e6","tid":1425741,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4efdd4d03975632d5f2abc8dbfdb6ace5c923fd8","tid":1425741,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:09:13.000Z","msg":"有冇平醫生推薦 睇唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:11:02.000Z","msg":"我仲研究緊 主要想捱過咗呢關先 其他嘢之後再算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0242bc61253b3fdff2e6562bcb87a3b6628f257","tid":1425741,"uid":264863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e51a235a4fb114d99926e3e6dd0e0d1528014e6","tid":1425741,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4efdd4d03975632d5f2abc8dbfdb6ace5c923fd8","tid":1425741,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:09:13.000Z","msg":"有冇平醫生推薦 睇唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:11:02.000Z","msg":"我仲研究緊 主要想捱過咗呢關先 其他嘢之後再算<i